# Classroom — laptop

APKs only from `phoenix-forge-classroom-forge-profile/{forge-profile-app,student-app,teacher-app}`.

Never build `teacher-edition/android/` or `student-edition/android/`.

```bash
source ~/.phoenix-forge/env.sh
build compile-classroom
build profile | student | teacher | classroom
```

After doc/path edits: `./scripts/cline-essence-drift-check.sh`

Schedule: **only** `docs/roadmaps/00_MASTER_ROADMAP.md`. See `phoenix-forge-universal.mdc`.
